Subject: [PATCH] Add coaching request form

- Request form inside #coaching for 1-to-1 / group coaching selection
- Captures name, address, age, email, contact number, badminton level
- Optional conditions field for illness / injury / past experience
- mailto submit handler matching the volunteer form pattern

